{
    "_comment": "Claude desktop (Linux) reports its tray icon as 'image-missing' after a 2026 update and sometimes registers twice. Draw our own logo and keep one. Right-click forwards to Claude's real menu (Show App / Quit); Claude ignores left-click, so we synthesise it via the window class.",
    "match": "claude",
    "base": "claude",
    "collapse": true,
    "wmclass": "claude"
}
